      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus, yield strength, and UTS from 15 coupon specimens per lot. Geometry verified by CMM to within 0.02 mm. One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis showed yield strength dominant parameter; uncertainty propagated to QoI uncertainty budget. Level 3 achieved."
    },
