      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717. No variation in loading rate or environmental condition (dry, room temperature only). This limitation reduces achieved level to 2, below required level of 3. Noted as gap in overall credibility argument."
